{
  "stem": "10710.3",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But you know, you used to go-- in the beginning, I used to wear short sleeve.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In the subway, people used to look then.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I decided, well, I have to show it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I wear long sleeve, and I got to the habit that I always wear long sleeves.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "From Plaszow, we went to Gross Rosen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a whole story before I went to Gross Rosen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Schindler [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] wanted to take-- wanted to take his factory and move it to Czechoslovakia, to Brunnlitz, which was the [INAUDIBLE] in the area.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now, everybody wanted to go get on that list.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He had a thousand people who wanted that list-- who wanted to be-- I mean, he wanted to take thousand people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And what he wanted to do, to take is all the people from Emalia, where we worked for him, he wants to take them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Those are his people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were being called Schindler's-- Schindler's people.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as soon as the people, the [NON-ENGLISH], the police, the Jewish police, found out that they were going to be transported, they wanted to be on the list.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And there was a guy, Marcel Goldberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was an alderman, and he took money from people.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They had money, they had diamonds, they had gold, still, in Plaszow, to put them on the list and took out other people who were supposed to go.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "One day, we were standing in Apellplatz, and they were taking-- calling the names for these people to go to Brunnlitz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "If you-- you knew if you go to Brunnlitz, you-- you may have a chance to survive.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Because the rest of the people were sent to-- to other camps-- Dachau, and they were sent to all kind of extermination camps.",
      "word_count": 23
    }
  ],
